Positive feedback</gtr:impact><gtr:outcomeId>55d703cdb78f24.54537629</gtr:outcomeId><gtr:partOfOfficialScheme>false</gtr:partOfOfficialScheme><gtr:primaryAudience>Public/other audiences</gtr:primaryAudience><gtr:url>http://foodis.org.uk/words-on-food-waste/who-is-responsible-for-household-food-waste/</gtr:url><gtr:year>2015</gtr:year></gtr:disseminationOutput><gtr:disseminationOutput><gtr:description>Member of research team wrote a project-related blog</gtr:description><gtr:form>A magazine, newsletter or online publication</gtr:form><gtr:geographicReach>National</gtr:geographicReach><gtr:id>42424CC4-8220-4C7B-A216-781FC0402994</gtr:id><gtr:impact>Stimulated discussion

Stakeholders got in touch</gtr:impact><gtr:outcomeId>54649e7215c662.04579745</gtr:outcomeId><gtr:partOfOfficialScheme>false</gtr:partOfOfficialScheme><gtr:primaryAudience>Public/other audiences</gtr:primaryAudience><gtr:url>http://blog.policy.manchester.ac.uk/sci-tech/2014/06/the-food-waste-crisis/</gtr:url><gtr:year>2014</gtr:year></gtr:disseminationOutput></gtr:disseminationOutputs><gtr:exploitationOutputs/><gtr:furtherFundingOutputs/><gtr:impactSummaryOutputs><gtr:impactSummaryOutput><gtr:description>- The project's final report was cited by the Institute of Grocery Distribution as part of their work on reducing food waste: 

